Package: ciel-sot-agent
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: _DEB_ARCH_
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-venv
Maintainer: Adrian Lipa <adrianlipa90@example.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/AdrianLipa90/CIEL-_SOT_Agent
Description: CIEL SOT Agent — Integration kernel and Quiet Orbital Control GUI
 CIEL SOT Agent is an integration kernel, synchronisation runtime,
 orbital bridge, and Sapiens interaction layer for the CIEL ecosystem.
 .
 Includes the Flask-based Quiet Orbital Control web interface and
 a GGUF model manager for on-device language model inference.
 .
 The application is installed into an isolated virtual environment at
 /opt/ciel-sot-agent/venv using pre-bundled wheels — no internet
 access is required during installation.
 .
 Supports Linux Mint 21+ and Ubuntu 22.04+.
